'''Hangar 9''' was a secretive hangar on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its owners allowed it to be used for illegal activities, and even put out advertisements in [[HoloNet News/Legends|''HoloNet News'']] suggesting it could be used so. It was also available for more legitimate uses, such as parking.

